<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PetHabit AI | Premium Nutrition Tracking</title>
    <style>
        /* VETERAN DEV NOTES: 
           - Use 'cubic-bezier' for "VC-level" smoothness (feels more natural than 'ease').
           - Dark mode with gold/teal accents signals "Premium/Enterprise".
           - High use of backdrop-filter for the modern 'Glass' look.
        */

        :root {
            --bg-dark: #080c14;
            --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --accent-gold: #cfa861;
            --accent-teal: #00d2d3;
            --text-main: #f0f2f5;
            --text-dim: #94a3b8;
            --bezier: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--text-main);
            overflow-x: hidden;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* --- Animated Background Orb --- */
        .orb {
            position: fixed;
            width: 600px;
            height: 600px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(207, 168, 97, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            top: -200px;
            right: -100px;
            z-index: -1;
            animation: float 20s infinite alternate var(--bezier);
        }

        @keyframes float {
            from { transform: translate(0, 0); }
            to { transform: translate(-100px, 100px); }
        }

        /* --- Navigation --- */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1.5rem 10%;
            background: rgba(8, 12, 20, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
        }

        /* --- Hero Section --- */
        .hero {
            padding: 120px 10% 80px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            background: var(--glass);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-teal);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            animation: fadeInDown 0.8s var(--bezier);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, #94a3b8 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s var(--bezier);
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
            animation: fadeInUp 1.2s var(--bezier);
        }

        /* --- VC Level Cards --- */
        .dashboard-preview {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 4rem;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--glass);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 24px;
            transition: all 0.4s var(--bezier);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--accent-gold);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
        }

        /* --- Nutrition Tracker UI Mockup --- */
        .tracker-bar {
            height: 8px;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .progress {
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--accent-teal);
            width: 0%;
            animation: loadProgress 2s 1s forwards var(--bezier);
        }

        @keyframes loadProgress {
            to { width: 75%; }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .cta-button {
            padding: 16px 32px;
            background: var(--accent-gold);
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(207, 168, 97, 0.4);
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="orb"></div>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">PETHABIT AI</div>
        <a href="#" class="cta-button" style="padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 0.9rem;">Join Waitlist</a>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <span class="badge">Next-Gen Pet Wellness</span>
        <h1>Nutrition Intelligence for Your Best Friend.</h1>
        <p>The first automated habit tracker for pets. Monitor nutrition, analyze caloric intake, and predict health trends with clinical precision.</p>
        
        <a href="#" class="cta-button">Get Early Access</a>

        <div class="dashboard-preview">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Smart Nutrition</h3>
                <p>Real-time analysis of ingredient quality for dogs and cats.</p>
                <div class="tracker-bar"><div class="progress" style="background: var(--accent-gold);"></div></div>
                <small style="color:var(--text-dim); display:block; margin-top:10px;">Proteins: 88% Optimal</small>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Habit Tracker</h3>
                <p>Monitor feeding consistency and hydration levels automatically.</p>
                <div class="tracker-bar"><div class="progress"></div></div>
                <small style="color:var(--text-dim); display:block; margin-top:10px;">Hydration Level: Stable</small>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Predictive Health</h3>
                <p>AI-driven insights to catch nutrition gaps before they affect vitality.</p>
                <div style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--accent-teal);">98.4%</div>
                <small style="color:var(--text-dim);">Accuracy Score</small>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
